Interface Stack<E>

Type Parameters:
E - the type of elements in this stack
All Superinterfaces:
Collection<E>, Iterable<E>, Iterable<E>
All Known Implementing Classes:
ArrayStack
interface Stack<E> extends Collection<E>
A stack is a collection of elements, with the last element added being the first one to be removed (LIFO).
